        {
            "title": "麻雀女王追男仔｜高海寧首現身謝票場畀一樣嘢嚇親 馬國明承諾出席更多場次派歡樂",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"麻雀女王追男仔｜高海寧首現身謝票場畀一樣嘢嚇親 馬國明承諾出席更多場次派歡樂\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7aae56e2c4535086fbdbab06ec872bf2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250204/_2025020416030381789.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">麻雀女王追男仔｜高海寧首現身謝票場畀一樣嘢嚇親 馬國明承諾出席更多場次派歡樂</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>高海寧（高Ling）、馬國明首度現身，聯同導演葉念琛為主演的蛇年賀歲片《麻雀女王追男仔》謝票，觀眾反應熱烈，高Ling笑指嚇親︰「我覺得觀眾好熱情呀！頭先一入戲院佢哋就歡呼歡迎我哋，我覺得可以多啲謝票，等我哋可以多啲互動，同埋可以同觀眾『恭喜發財』吖嘛！」\n\n</p><h2>高海寧由美返港即殺入戲院多戲影迷</h2>\n<p>在場的粉絲高舉大牌及應援物品，齊心祝賀偶像：「祝《麻雀女王追男仔》票房大賣！」高Ling、馬國明相當「寵粉」，於戲院大堂跟觀眾逐一合照，以致人龍打爆戲院，令現場水洩不通。馬國明表示：「最開心見到觀眾睇得好開心，睇完戲又好開心，感受到電影喺新年帶到歡樂畀大家，好有滿足感！」高Ling當日早上從美國工作返港，甫落機即加入謝票相當有心，她與馬國明呼籲觀眾繼續入場支持，後者預告會現身更多謝票場次。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章︰<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/film-drama/3424737/%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%A9%E5%BE%97%E6%84%8F%E7%94%9FB%E9%9A%A8%E7%B7%A3-%E8%A2%AB%E9%AB%98%E6%B5%B7%E5%AF%A7%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86%E9%9D%9A%E6%B9%AF%E9%81%A0%E8%B7%9D%E5%8F%AB%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E8%B6%85%E8%B2%BC%E5%BF%83-%E7%94%B1%E6%8B%8D%E5%8A%87%E5%88%B0%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E9%BB%98%E5%A5%91%E5%8D%81%E8%B6%B3\">馬國明愛情事業兩得意生B隨緣 被高海寧踢爆靚湯遠距叫外賣超貼心 由拍劇到電影默契十足</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058877/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"右起馬國明、葉念琛，高海寧美國工作回港即親身謝票。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3ef757faa726e21787d0ccf940173803/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-04_at_15_28_16.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        右起馬國明、葉念琛，高海寧美國工作回港即親身謝票。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058878/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馬國明表示感受觀眾熱情︰「好有滿足感！」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ea9f404100e409fe1be0e0b1e078b4b/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-04_at_15_28_17_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬國明表示感受觀眾熱情︰「好有滿足感！」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058879/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"賀歲片《麻雀女王追男仔》賣情懷、大堆頭。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2fd9376605eded1d352b354e6538b1df/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-04_at_15_28_17_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        賀歲片《麻雀女王追男仔》賣情懷、大堆頭。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058880/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馬國明、